{"tid":1675490,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"［觀賞用］代步 滑板車 討論區","createTime":"2019-10-26T02:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T07:37:00.000Z","uid":75218,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"829715f78235f58759610613d16e00e263ec285e","tid":1675490,"uid":75218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T02:39:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根據《道路交通條例》（香港法例第 374 章），「汽車」的定義為任何由機械驅動的車輛。小型電單車、電動輔助單車、電動滑板車及電動單輪車等電動可移動工具，均屬機械驅動，因此都屬於「汽車」，必須領牌才可於道路行駛。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n黨鐵日日玩停駛，步兵行一星期叫做身心健康，玩足一個月我呢d大西北居民真係行到腳都殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fqHNTPj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqHNTPj.jpg&h=7714fd96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fae952ea616264e1164bb33238192da6a15b77ca","tid":1675490,"uid":152790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"轉車帶住？"},{"pid":"3514a9994d220eabcecfd4a63bdb120ff936c055","tid":1675490,"uid":75218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fae952ea616264e1164bb33238192da6a15b77ca","tid":1675490,"uid":152790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"轉車帶住？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"摺埋，手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0227e12b867e948cb1d32982a3c01e5ee94609c","tid":1675490,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"想問吓張相邊度黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27290b10b693f4fbb4e4a4ad79901491da3e7c3a","tid":1675490,"uid":75218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0227e12b867e948cb1d32982a3c01e5ee94609c","tid":1675490,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"想問吓張相邊度黎<img src=\"/assets/fa